text: The textures above are used by the game for drawing blocks, even though some of these blocks cannot be normally obtained.
Due to being based on Java Edition Beta 1.3's terrain.png, the above textures are present, but are not yet used by any blocks in the game.
The lava and water placeholder textures are used as actual fluid textures in many cases (although on some devices water looked like java water at the time).
Added two new textures for the info update blocks.
The game now uses the textures for cactus.
The textures have been updated to Java Edition 1.0.0 and has inherited the additions and changes made to terrain.png. The above ported texture changes apply to blocks existent in the game.
The above ported texture changes do not apply to any existing blocks.
The newly added textures above do not yet belong to any blocks.
The ice texture has been made completely opaque.
The game now uses the textures for Oak Door,Oak Fence and Oak Fence Gate.
The game now uses the textures of bookshelf.
The iron door textures have changed.
info_update now has a completely transparent pixel in the top left.
The game now uses the textures for crafting tables.
The game now uses the textures for sapling, furnace and glass pane.
The game now uses the textures for chest (excluding double) and bed.
Added textures for glowing obsidian and the nether reactor core.
the game now uses the textures for glowstone,melon and melon stems.
The grass block side texture has changed.
Textures for the stonecutter and sandstone and quartz block variants have been added.
the game now uses the textures for netherrack and nether brick.
Added textures for spruce planks, birch planks, beetroot seeds, Carrots, Potatoes, hay bales and the block of coal.
The game now uses the textures for pumpkins,iron bars,rails,powered rails and sponges.
Added textures for cocoa, tripwire and command blocks, despite these not yet being implemented.
The iron door has been repaired and the grass block side texture reverted.
The cactus top texture has unintentionally changed.
terrain.png has been removed, and block textures have been relocated to terrain-atlas.tga.

Added the textures of podzol,tall grass,peony,lilac,rose bushes,sunflowers,hardened clay (all 16 colours),Acacia Wood,Dark Oak Wood,blue orchid,allium,azure bluet,tulip (all 4 colours),sapling (jungle,acacia and dark oak variety),Red sand,andesite,granite,Diorite (polish versions),Emerald Block,Emerald Ore and Packed Ice.
the game now uses the textures for mycelium,Mushroom Blocks, mushroom stem,cocoa,end portal frames,lily pads and end stone.
Added the texture for grass paths and redstone blocks.
The game now uses the textures for enchanting tables,brewing stands,soul sand and nether wart.
Added the texture of Anvil,Chipped Anvil,Damaged Anvil,Flower Pots and Nether Quartz Ore.
The game now uses the textures for redstones,redstone torches,levers,tripwires and detector rails.
Detector rails now have a unique texture for when activated.
Powered Rails no longer always on.
Added the texture for redstone lamps,daylight sensors,activator rail,5 wooden doors versions and iron trapdoor.
Added the textures for redstone Comparator,dropper,Hopper,item frame,Red sandstone and slime blocks.
The game now uses the textures for dispenser,but with a different texture.
The games now uses the textures for repeaters and cauldron.
the game now uses the textures for pistons and sticky piston.
Peony and rose bushes now have textures from the Legacy Console Edition.
Textures for the allow, deny, border, sea lantern, wet sponge and Prismarine blocks have been added.
textures for beacons has been added.
textures for Chorus Flowers, chorus plants, End gateways, end stone bricks, end rods, dragon eggs, Purpur blocks and Purpur Pillars Has been Added.
textures for command blocks has been added.
Added textures for sixteen colors each of concrete, concrete powder, glazed terracotta and frosted ice.
The textures of four glazed terracotta blocks have changed.
The exclusive 3D Export structure block, jukeboxes, Coarse Dirt, stained glass and stained glass panes has been added.
Added stripped logs. The spruce and dark oak logs have exclusive side textures.
textures for blue ice, coral blocks, coral fans, corals, dead coral blocks, dead coral fan, dried kelp blocks and 5 types of trapdoors.
textures for sea pickles has been added.
The two exclusive top textures have changed.
Added textures for bubble columns and turtle eggs.
Added the texture for bamboo and Scaffolding.
Added the textures for cornflowers, lily of the valleys and smooth stone.
Added the textures for barrel, bells, cartography tables, fletching table, grindstone, smithing Table, smokers and lanterns.
Updated a huge amount of textures.
Added the textures for Composters, campfires and Lecterns.
Changed texture for some new crafting stations.
Added textures for Nether Update blocks.
Added the textures for more Nether Update blocks.
Change the following texture to match Java Edition.
The textures of crimson and warped doors have been changed.
Added the texture for powder snow.
Added textures for sculk sensors and pointed dripstone.
Added textures for blocks of copper, cut copper, copper ore and lightning rods.
Added the texture for dripstone blocks.
Updated the textures of all of the Overworld ores.
Added the textures for moss block, glow berries, big dripleaf, small dripleaf, spore blossom, azalea leaves, hanging roots, rooted dirt and azaleas.
The texture for glow lichens has been added.
Added textures for cobbled deepslate, deepslate, polished deepslate, deepslate bricks, deepslate tiles, and deepslate ores.
The textures of coal ore, diamond ore, gold ore, and iron ore have been changed.
Added the textures for amethyst buds, amethyst clusters, blocks of amethyst, blocks of raw metal, budding amethyst, calcite, glow item frames, smooth basalt, tinted glass, tuff.
The textures of blackstone, gilded blackstone, deepslate coal ore, deepslate copper ore, deepslate lapis lazuli ore, snowy grass blocks, and smokers have been updated.
Changed the textures of blocks of raw metal and deepslate.
Added unused textures for sculk, sculk catalyst, sculk shrieker, sculk vein.
Changed the textures of glow berries and powered redstone comparator.
Changed the textures of Carrot Age 3 and cartography table.
Added the texture for Frog Spawn.
Changed the textures of frog spawn.
Added the texture for reinforced deepslate.

texts.text: This article is about all changes made to block textures. For the texture atlas that housed all block textures prior to Java Edition 1.5 and Pocket Edition v0.8.0 alpha, see terrain.png.

This page document the history of the textures of blocks, their additions, changes and removals. Additions and changes made to the models of blocks, as well as any new blocks which reuse prior textures, will not be documented here.
